  "detailed_description": "<h1>Curator Reviews</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/3bfac521dc7cb4d36d39b3c93a95f724.avif?t=1756060239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras_big/3bfac521dc7cb4d36d39b3c93a95f724.avif?t=1756060239 width=800 height=149 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/a4051544d7acdd2ab74d9ab3002c3d9e.avif?t=1756060239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras_big/a4051544d7acdd2ab74d9ab3002c3d9e.avif?t=1756060239 width=800 height=149 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep Space Directive is a base-building and resource management game about expanding, exploring, building, upgrading, and of course, defending. Your directive is to generate corporate profit by expanding and exploiting the resources in the world around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/cc63389b02f06edb47f9811b5ed17b09.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/63bcc008ac9c1a45f41935264c8ea50c.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/63bcc008ac9c1a45f41935264c8ea50c.webm?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/63bcc008ac9c1a45f41935264c8ea50c.mp4?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build supply chains of mines and power sources to feed your hungry smelters, factories and refineries. The corporation demands profits and rising stock prices!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/e2a13baa047c0ee07d56001d676f5d2f.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/ee0c91b89770f45578675684211b18e1.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/ee0c91b89770f45578675684211b18e1.webm?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/ee0c91b89770f45578675684211b18e1.mp4?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A constant stream of fuel cells and raw resources are needed to keep your defenses functioning and your colonists fed.  Collect, refine, and process resources. Fuel cells and ore are needed for buildings and colonists need water and food. As your population grows you can support more and more buildings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/ef8f614212c5008f612efcfc0d89365f.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/c42c53b8e50223844fc66b3410a97c63.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/c42c53b8e50223844fc66b3410a97c63.webm?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/c42c53b8e50223844fc66b3410a97c63.mp4?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were sent to build mines and factories, but when you landed you discovered it wasn't that easy.  How will you defend your base? Powerful stationary towers or mobile but weaker units? Keep your energy supplies topped up before night falls or risk destruction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9f761087eb5d3d133f2f402bb608c304.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9ee3c0a7fa2eee335f220ad471e4637b.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9ee3c0a7fa2eee335f220ad471e4637b.webm?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9ee3c0a7fa2eee335f220ad471e4637b.mp4?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemies are more that just a drain on your resources. The Terrene resource dropped by the enemies can be used to help expand outward to find new resources.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep Space Directive is a base-building and resource management game about expanding, exploring, building, upgrading, and of course, defending. Your directive is to generate corporate profit by expanding and exploiting the resources in the world around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/cc63389b02f06edb47f9811b5ed17b09.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/63bcc008ac9c1a45f41935264c8ea50c.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/63bcc008ac9c1a45f41935264c8ea50c.webm?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/63bcc008ac9c1a45f41935264c8ea50c.mp4?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build supply chains of mines and power sources to feed your hungry smelters, factories and refineries. The corporation demands profits and rising stock prices!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/e2a13baa047c0ee07d56001d676f5d2f.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/ee0c91b89770f45578675684211b18e1.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=