pan class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9f761087eb5d3d133f2f402bb608c304.webp?t=1756060239\" width=605 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9ee3c0a7fa2eee335f220ad471e4637b.poster.avif?t=1756060239\" width=606 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9ee3c0a7fa2eee335f220ad471e4637b.webm?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2510180/extras/9ee3c0a7fa2eee335f220ad471e4637b.mp4?t=1756060239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemies are more that just a drain on your resources. The Terrene resource dropped by the enemies can be used to help expand outward to find new resources.</p>",
